            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>GIS-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6456:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6456\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6456-TW</a>)15日12:00上漲6.3元，股價漲停報70.1元，委買553張，成交36,242張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為觸控及顯示模組之生產及銷售業務。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>GIS-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6456:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6456\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6456-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲16%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲9.23%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-1,496 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-1,724 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：-1 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+229 張</li> <li>融資增減：+3,586 張</li> <li>融券增減：+100 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
